Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:51.54,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming back here, no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:53.82,Ep Title,Next Title 2,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(170,1)}Next Episode\NLeave Letter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.54,0:23:53.82,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us, and one critter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:57.91,Side Bar Top Pink,TextR,0000,0000,0000,,A leave letter even \Nthough we just started?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:57.91,Side Bar Bottom Pink,TextL,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason deeper\Nthan the universe for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:05.00,Side Bar Top Pink,TextR,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow or the other,\Nthe Battle on Rakuyo Arc has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:05.00,Side Bar Bottom Pink,TextL,0000,0000,0000,,What's "Rakuyo"?? Find out next time!